  - Application: Agricultural lands, coastlines, mines
  - Rate: 1 ton mineral removes 1.25 tons CO₂
  - Cost: $50/ton CO₂ at scale
  - Deployment: 100 sites globally by 2031
  - Total Capacity: 10 million tons CO₂/year

Optimization:
  - Material Selection: Quantum chemistry for optimal minerals
