Manufacturing and Deployment:
  - Production: 10,000 nodes/month
  - Installation: 5,000 nodes/month
  - Cost: $10,000 per node at scale
  - Total Cost: $1B for 100,000 nodes
  - Timeline: 20 months to manufacture and deploy
```

