Implementation:
  - Architecture: Hierarchical with emergent global intelligence
  - Learning: Continuous across all nodes and time scales
  - Governance: Distributed with human oversight
  - Evolution: Capability improves without explicit reprogramming

Metrics:
  - Response Time: < 1 ms for local, < 1 second for global
