  - Quantum: +20 (applications focus)
  - Neuromorphic: +15 (applications focus)
  - Energy Systems: +30 (markets, storage)
  - AI/ML: +20 (safety, specialized models)
  - Platform: +25 (security, scalability)
  - Operations: +30 (global deployment prep)
  - Business: +10 (sales, marketing, partnerships)

Q3-Q4 2025: Scale Up (250 people, total 500)
  - Quantum: +50 (manufacturing, scale)
  - Neuromorphic: +40 (manufacturing, scale)
  - Energy Systems: +50 (international expansion)
  - AI/ML: +30 (scale, optimization)
