  - ISO 45001: Occupational health and safety (2026)

Technology Industry:
  - ISO 27001: Information security management (2025)
  - ISO 27017: Cloud security (2026)
  - ISO 27018: Cloud privacy (2026)
  - SOC 2: Trust services criteria (2026)

Quantum-Specific:
  - NIST Post-Quantum Cryptography Standards (as released)
  - Quantum Random Number Generator Standards (2026)
  - Quantum Key Distribution Standards (2027)
```

